2026-06-01T11:10:19.1916576Z 246            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-06-01T11:10:19.1917296Z 247            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-06-01T11:10:19.1918030Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-06-01T11:10:19.1918762Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-06-01T11:10:19.1919383Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-06-01T11:10:19.1920037Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-06-01T11:10:19.1921009Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-06-01T11:10:19.1921729Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-06-01T11:10:19.1922433Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-06-01T11:10:19.1922990Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
