2026-06-01T11:10:19.5402294Z 54        is cancelled as soon as the user switches apps and the completion
2026-06-01T11:10:19.5402549Z 55        notification is never shown. The timer is declared as a
2026-06-01T11:10:19.5402861Z 56        mediaPlayback foreground service because Samsung One UI suppresses
2026-06-01T11:10:19.5403153Z 57        FOREGROUND_SERVICE_SPECIAL_USE notifications, preventing the
2026-06-01T11:10:19.5403425Z 58        ongoing countdown notification from appearing on those devices.
